Hey,How old am I, I am in my early 20s. How am I, I am fed up with my old glasses, other than that, I'm fine thank you. My name is Hazel Genius

The reason I have come for a sight test today is because I think my current glasses are getting quite old and I would like some new ones. I am not having any issues or problems seeing with my current glasses, both up close and far away all seems good to me, but I just really would like some new frames these ones are feeling quite worn now.
